tika.dc.description: Party in a Cup! has all the secret ingredients girls need to throw 4 unforgettable parties—a slumber party, tea party, summer party, and spa party. This cookbook comes with easy-to-follow recipes for 25 totally tasty treats, party favors, and decorating ideas. Party-planning has never tasted so good!
